------------------------------1. Install and explore the OpenGL -------------------------------------


dharmendra@pandit:~$ sudo apt-get update

dharmendra@pandit:~$ sudo apt-get install libglut libglu1-mesa-dev freeeglu3-dev mesa-common-dev

dharmendra@pandit:~$ sudo apt install g++

For Compilation

g++ filename.cpp -lGL -lGLU -lglut

For Execution
./a.out
